.SH NAME
shelly-lora-status - Show LoRa add-on status


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBshelly lora status  [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Show LoRa add-on status for a Shelly device.

.PP
Displays the current LoRa configuration and signal quality
information from the last received packet.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for status

.PP
\fB--id\fP=100
	LoRa component ID

.PP
\fB--json\fP[=false]
	Output as JSON


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
\fB--config\fP=""
